				<td colspan="2"><span>Bards are so underappreciated it isnt funny.  My main is a 59 pally and I just love having bards in LDON.  absolutly love them.  what they bring to the table is so more then people realize.  
<br />

<br />
Well anyways on to my point, I went ahead and made a bard and just got him to 37 the last 2 weeks.  most ldon groups have asked me to pull, crowd control, and be ML, not only that i constantly twist at least 3 songs in the mix.  Through this all everyone keeps bashing bards.  It makes no sense to me.  Being a tank at 59 i loved bards so much and appreciated their DS and haste and loved their pulling as it was a constant stream and near perfection.  But all i hear from everyone is how worthless bards are and of course every caster loves to say &quot;Play mana song&quot; when it has obviously been playing through their whole rant.  It' just nuts.  So A quick question I guess.  What is a bard to do?  Why is there no respect?  /rant off
<br />
</span></td>
