				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Wow.. Just wow 37 bard<a name="27889"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 15 04 5:18 PM</span></td>
