				<td colspan="2"><span>The problem is that many players just don't understand bards.
<br />
They don't understand what bards can do, when they are doing it or how they are doing it? 
<br />

<br />
Even in a guild that has cleared POTime, we have members who think a bard's only job on raids is playing marr and AE resists. Some that think a bard is best used as a wizard group damage focus item or a rogue group overhaste buff.
<br />

<br />

<br />
The overall ignorance, at all levels, of what bards can do is utterly mindblowing.
<br />

<br />

<br />
A favorite quote from a Bard FAQ:
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">-Why [insert any question here]? 
<br />

<br />
